Meanwhile, as they were saying this, behind-the-scenes Chinese officials were working frantically to destroy relevant evidence of where it actually came from.
In their initial statements, Chinese officials claimed that a lightning strike had caused that crash.
Chinese media meanwhile were ordered to ignore the crash entirely except for “positive news” or … news issued by authorities.
“Racism is not the right tool to cover your own incompetence” lectured Chinese state media when President Trump refer to the Wuhan virus.
American media parroted that line almost precisely, as no doubt Chinese expected they would.